window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Throughout time, from ancient Rome to modern Britain, the great empires built and maintained their domination through force of arms and political power.</p> <p>But not the United States.</p> <p>America has dominated the world in a new, peaceful, and pervasive way - through the continued creation of staggering wealth. In this authoritative, engrossing history, John Steele Gordon captures as never before the true source of our nation's global influence: wealth and the capacity to create more of it.</p>"; 
